00:05:16.139 --> 00:05:17.732
It's actually almost an exact number

00:05:17.732 --> 00:05:19.674
because of the way that
this is just a parabola,

00:05:19.674 --> 00:05:21.364
so we can actually do this.

00:05:21.364 --> 00:05:22.218
But anyway,

00:05:22.218 --> 00:05:23.813
this is fairly straightforward.

00:05:23.813 --> 00:05:24.403
Once again,

00:05:24.403 --> 00:05:26.692
our change in quantity is 2,

00:05:26.692 --> 00:05:29.468
and our change in total revenue,

00:05:29.468 --> 00:05:31.122
our change in total revenue is,

00:05:31.122 --> 00:05:32.375
we're going from 5 to 9,

